commit message: Update setools-android submodule to latest version 1.2 (Android 6 support)
Build included setools-android for more architectures (arm64-v8a, mips64, x86_64)
Shutdown instead of reboot after too many failed unlock attempts
Add support for CyanogenMod 13 (different 'vdc cryptfs changepw' format)
Replace oldPassword with 'default_password' if it is empty (better safe than sorry)
